{"tid":1212272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"{意見統一} 野餐定一齊搭港鐵","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:41:28.000Z","uid":259642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2d15d72ac0662fa1f068e1c7567efc50fcba6d","tid":1212272,"uid":259642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"見到大家話要去搞港鐵 <br />\n但係同時間都應該會有人留守金鐘<br />\n如果真係比大家癱瘓港鐵，咁喺金鐘嗰班就會孤立無援<br />\n坦白講唔建議大家再留守甚至衝金鐘，今日已經要清場清得咁盡就知<br />\n聽日如果有人再衝分分鐘會戒嚴，到時就好嚴重<br />\n最後，想去野餐嘅唔好再衝，圍住立法會同政總就夠，唔好比籍口啲狗打，我知啲狗好狼死，大家見唔對路就要撤<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以比啲意見⋯⋯成個人好亂"},{"pid":"c9c851903a75fac91d163dbfbb8096a83b4b3a93","tid":1212272,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da02d360a22ce1335a95da4ef4fd26dfbf29a072","tid":1212272,"uid":22894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:54:17.000Z","msg":"呢個係來自一班鐵膠嘅呼籲<br />\n搭車要摸清楚緊急設備 免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90M7Cew.png&h=40abe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBp5oUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBp5oUx.png&h=7917b9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1PMSNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1PMSNN.png&h=d9ef5a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a50cd820eb47b8abaa37916d88dd15cad421837","tid":1212272,"uid":183631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"你係個集入邊，就一定要上果一架車？月台咁細，企滿個月台，大家咁啱唔想搭呢架車，係都要等下一㗎，唔可以？我次次入去都等幾架車先入嘅，有是坐得舒服，坐返半個鐘添啊！<br />\n揀幾個重點月台，一啲都唔難。"},{"pid":"7e3ccc29f4412c03bf001d853c2e0f460c7916fa","tid":1212272,"uid":183631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"入左去嘅人，跟從鐵膠嘅呼籲。成件事根本上就易過借火。"},{"pid":"f5a5db7df09b532866e3b5d1dfaeba7c62e0f123","tid":1212272,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:08:50.000Z","msg":"搭鐵嘅話就注意安全同守法<br />\n<br />\n[連鎖反應][蝴蝶效應]或者再解釋一下鐵路嘅重要性[請廣傳]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1211783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1211783</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1adee6b26ddbdd2baf34231e1b801aefe66ca77d","tid":1212272,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:23:10.000Z","msg":"立會開會要幾個鐘前通知？"},{"pid":"14cce259ccc0c4f367c5e43f24dd0682b19f3003","tid":1212272,"uid":259642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1adee6b26ddbdd2baf34231e1b801aefe66ca77d","tid":1212272,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:23:10.000Z","msg":"立會開會要幾個鐘前通知？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"唔清楚，應該冇特定<br />\n你睇今日就知，幾時清到場就通知⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b57077d6a9d81af5d4c725c8dee29e239d25a","tid":1